   Special Notice:
     * NEW Impact of the Events of September 11, 2001, on BLS Nonfarm
       Payroll Series for States and Metropolitan Areas.
     * UPDATED Impact of the Events of September 11, 2001, on BLS Nonfarm
       Payroll Employment Series
     * Employment in Areas of Manhattan Affected by the Events of
       September 11, 2001
     * Notice of Revisions to Nevada Seasonally adjusted data: The Nevada
       seasonally adjusted estimates for total nonfarm, manufacturing, and
       nondurable manufacturing industries were revised on March 29th.
       Data were revised for January and February, 2001

